	<div class="wpb_text_column wpb_content_element " >
		<div class="wpb_wrapper">
			<div>The client and his neighbor are starting a small homebrew adventure (making beer) and are looking to design the logo, the beer label, and potentially other marketing pieces. They are brewing the beer in one of their garages as would love for the garage to somehow be represented in the logo.</div>
<div></div>
<div>It should be clever, clean and engaging. If this product ever makes it to a grocery store shelf, it will be competing with all the other microbrews.</div>

